node js install instructions:

1. goto: nodejs.org
2. Click Download
3. Click Macintosh Installer
4. When the install has finished downloading, launch it by Double-clcking on node-v0.6.19.pkg (or the most recent version)
5. Installation Wizard:
	- Introduction: click Continue
	- Installation Type: click Install
	- Enter your password when prompted
	- Click close when installation is complete
6. Open Terminal (Applications/Utilities/Terminal)
	- when terminal opens (you're now using the command line) type 'node -v' (without the quotes) and hit the Enter key.
	- You should see 'v0.6.19' printed (or the more recent version you downloaded)
